00:24:15.230 --> 00:24:18.290
and hadn't probably talked about
in a while-- hadn't had anyone

00:24:18.290 --> 00:24:20.030
to talk about it within a while.

00:24:20.030 --> 00:24:22.700
And then this, I think,
this very beautiful song

00:24:22.700 --> 00:24:23.644
comes out of it.

00:24:23.644 --> 00:24:24.560
MICHAEL SHAYAN: Great.

00:24:24.560 --> 00:24:26.330
DAVID CROMER: But
that's the context.

00:24:26.330 --> 00:24:27.705
MICHAEL SHAYAN:
So please give it

