It's this-- it's
a breakfast food.

00:43:56.960 --> 00:43:59.120
It's basically layers
of dough and butter

00:43:59.120 --> 00:44:01.920
rolled, baked in the oven
overnight for like 12 hours.

00:44:01.920 --> 00:44:04.700
And you eat it with crushed
tomatoes and a hard boiled egg.

00:44:04.700 --> 00:44:07.040
12 Chairs in the West Village
has incredible jachnun

00:44:07.040 --> 00:44:09.442
on the weekends.

