00:44:14.380 --> 00:44:17.090
BILL ARMY: Oh, god.

00:44:17.090 --> 00:44:17.690
Hummus?

00:44:17.690 --> 00:44:20.432
[LAUGHTER]

00:44:21.444 --> 00:44:22.860
ARI'EL STACHEL:
My aunt's jachnun.

00:44:22.860 --> 00:44:24.400
[LAUGHTER]

00:44:24.400 --> 00:44:25.670
RACHEL PRATHER: Tabbouleh.

00:44:25.670 --> 00:44:27.190
KRISTEN SIEH: Oh, you took mine.

00:44:27.190 --> 00:44:28.540
